Name: UCSB
Description: A university in California located along the coast.

Name: Disneyland
Description: A theme park located in Southern California that is an amusement park that has fun for the whole family!

Name: USS Midway Museum
Description: A historical naval aircraft carrier museum located in downtown San Diego. It is a great museum that shows a large amount of aircraft and history of the Midway.

Name: Mount Rushmore
Description: Mount Rushmore is a national memorial carved into Mount Rushmore in the Black Hills region of South Dakota. This memorial is roughly 60ft high, depicting the faces of George Washington, Thomas Jefferson, Theodore Roosevelt, and Abraham Lincoln.

Name: Idyllwild
Description: An unicorporated community in the San Jacinto Mountains that my family has loved visiting for years. It is a beautiful destination, somewhere everyone should visit.

Name: Carlsbad Beach
Description: A surf beach located in Southern California, not to far from Legoland, and a place that I visited many times as a child with my family.
